    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the culture, styles, and period dating 220 to 280 CE, corresponding to Chinese history after the fall of the Han dynasty; marked by a  tripartite division of China between the states of Wei, Shu, and Wu.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
